hadiths[31]{hadithnumber,text}:
3770,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah ne farmaya jo shakhs apna hissey aazad karey barda mein se (yani wo barda mushtarak ho) aur aik Sharik apna hissey aazad karey aur phir aazad karne waley ke paas is qadr maal ho jo bardey ki qeemat ko pahunch ‌jaey to us bardey ki waajibi qeemat lagai jaey aur baqi sharikon ko in ke hissey ki qeemat iske maal main se di jaeygi aur kal barda uski taraf se aazad ho jaeyga ‌ aur jo wo maaldar na ho to jis qadr hissey us barda ka aazad hua itna hi aazad rahega. ‌
3771,isi hadis ki dusri asnaad mazkoor hain.
3772,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ‌ : jo barda 2 aadmiyon mein mushtarak ho phir aik Sharik apna hissey aazad kar dewe to wo zaamin hoga doosrey Sharik ke hissey ka (agar maal daar ho (
3773,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ‌ : jo shakhs apna hissey ghulam main aazad kar de to uska chhudana (yani doosrey hissey ka bhi aazad karna) bhi isi ke maal se hoga agar maaldaar ho, agar maaldaar na ho to ghulam mahnat mazduri karey aur is par jabr na karein  ."
3774,tarjama dusri riwayat ka bhi wahi hai jo uper guzra us main itna zyada hai ke agar wo aazad karne wala maaldaar na ho to ghulam ki waajibi qeemat lagai jaey aur mahnat karey apne baqi hissey ke liye jo aazad nahi hua magar is par jabr nahi hoga.
3775,Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne ‌ibne-abi Aruba ki hadis ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki aur hadis mein ye bhi zikr kya ke uski waajibi qeemat lagai jaey.
3776,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne aik londi khareed kar usey aazad karne ka irada kya. uske maalikon ne kaha : ham is shart par ye kaneez aapko bechengey ke iska haqe-'walaa' hamara hoga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne is baat ka zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap ne farmaya : ye ( shart ( tumhen ( usko khareed kar aazad karne se) na rokey (is kaneez ko zaroor aazadi milni chahiye) bila shubah 'walaa' ka haq usi ka hai jisne ( ghulam ya kaneez ko) aazad kya.
3777,"Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se riwayat ki, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke Barira (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aai. wo unse apni makaatibat ( qeemat ada karke aazaadi ka muaahida karne) ke silsiley mein madad maang rahi thi. us ne apni makaatibat ki raqam mein se kuchh bhi ada nahi kiya tha. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne us se kaha : apne maalikon ke paas jao, agar wo pasand karein ke main tumhari makaatibat (likhai) ki raqam ada karun aur tumhara haq 'walaa' mere liye ho, to main ( tumhari qeemat ki adaaeygi ( kar dun gi. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye apne maalikon se kahi to unhon-ne inkar kar diya, aur kaha : agar wo tumharey sath neki karna chahti hain to karein, lekin tumhari 'walaa' ka haq hamara hi hoga. is par unhon (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha : tum khareed lo aur aazad kar do, kyonke 'walaa' ka haq usi ka hai jisne aazad kiya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (member par) khadey huey aur farmaya : logon ko kya hua hai? wo aisi shartein rakhtey hain jo Allah ki kitab (ki taalimat ( mein nahi. jisne aisi shart rakhi jo Allah ki kitab mein nahi hai to usey iska koi haq nahi chahey wo sou martaba shart rakh ley. Allah ki shart zyada haq rakhti hai aur wahi zyada mazbut hai."
3778,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Barira (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas aai aur kehney lagi : Aaisha ! maine apne maalikon se nou (9) auqiya par makaatibat ( qeemat ki adaaeygi par aazad ho janey ka muaahida ( kiya hai, har saal mein aik auqiya ( 40 dirham ada karna ( hai, aagey Leis ki hadis ke ham mana hai aur (is mein) ye izafa kiya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhen unki ye baat ( Barira ko aazad karne se) na rokey . usey khareedo aur aazad kar do aur) Yunus ne) hadis mein kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon mein khadey huey, Allah ki hamd aur sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : ammaa ba'd ! (khutba diya jis mein shart wali baat irshad farmai.)."
3779,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Barira (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas aai aur kehney lagi : mere maalikon ne mere sath nou (9) saalon mein nou (9) auqiya (ki adaaeygi (ke badley makaatibat (aazadi ki baat ( ki hai. har saal mein aik auqiya ( ada karna ( hai. meri madad karein. maine us se kaha : agar tumharey Malik chaahein ke main unhein yak-musht gin dun aur tumhen aazad kar dun aur 'walaa' ka haq mera ho. to main aisa kar loongi. us ne ye baat apne maalikon se ki to unhon-ne (usey man-ney se) inkar kar diya siwaey-iske ke haq 'walaa' unka ho. iske baad wo mere paas aai aur ye baat mujhey batai, kaha : to maine is par barhami ka izhar kiya, aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! phir aisa nahi ho sakta. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye baat suni to mujh se poochha, maine aapko ( poori ( baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey khareedo aur aazad kar do, unke liye 'walaa' ki shart rakh lo, kyonke (asl mein to) 'walaa' (sarparasti) ka haq usi ka hai jisne aazad kiya. maine aisa hi kiya. kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sham ke waqt khutba diya, Allah ki hamd aur sana jo iske shaayaan shaan thi bayan ki, phir farmaya : ammaa ba'd! logon ko kya hua hai? wo aisi shartein rakhtey hain jo Allah ki kitab mein (jaaiz) nahi. jo bhi shart Allah ki kitab mein (rawaa) nahi, wo baatil hai, chahey wo sou (100) shartein hon, Allah ki kitab hi sabse sachchi aur Allah ki shart sabse mazbut hai. tum mein se kuchh logon ko kya hua hai? unmein se koi kehta hai : falan ko aazad tum karo aur haq 'walaa' mera hoga. ( halanke ( 'walaa' ka haq usi ka hai jisne aazad kiya."
3780,"ibne-Numair , Wakee aur Jarir sab ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath abu-Usama ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki, lekin Jarir ki hadis mein hai, kaha is ( Barira (Raziallahu anhu)) ka shauhar ghulam tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey ( shadi bar-qaraar rakhney ya na rakhney ke barey mein) ikhtiyar diya to usne khud ko) nikah ki bandish se aazad dekhnaa ( pasand kiya. agar uska shauhar aazad hota to aap usey ye ikhtiyar na detey, aur unki hadis mein ammaa ba'd ! ke alfaz nahi hain. (ye alfaz khutbey ki taraf ishara kartey hain.)"
3781,"Hisham-bin-Urwa ne hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke mamley mein teen faisley huey : uske maalikon ne chaha ke usey bech dein aur uske haq 'walaa' ko (apne liye) mashroot (shart ke saath) kar dein, maine ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai to aap ne farmaya : usey khareedo aur aazad kar do, kyonke 'walaa' usi ka haq hai jisne aazad kiya. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : wo aazad hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey ikhtiyar diya, us ne apni zaat (ko aazad rakhney) ka intikhab kiya. (hazrat Aaisha ne) kaha : log is par sadqa kartey they aur wo (us mein se kuchh ( hamein hadiya karti thi, maine ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kahi to aap ne farmaya : wo is par sadqa hai aur tum logon ke liye hadiya hai, lihaza usey kha liya karo."
3782,"Simak ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko Ansar ke logon se khareeda , unhon-ne 'walaa' ki shart lagai , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : 'walaa' (ka haq ( usi ke liye hai jisne ( aazaadi ki) nemat ka ehtimaam kiya. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey ikhtiyar diya. jabke uska shauhar ghulam tha. aur us ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko gosht hadiya kiya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum hamarey liye us gosht se ( saalan ( taiyaar kartin ? Hazrat Aaisha ne kaha : ye ( gosht ( Barira (Raziallahu anhu) par sadqa kiya gaya tha to aap ne farmaya : wo uske liye sadqa tha aur hamarey liye hadiya hai."
3783,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qasim se suna, wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke unhon-ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko aazad karne ke liye khareednaa chaha to un logon ( maalikon ( ne uski 'walaa' ki shart laga di. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne is baat ka tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kiya, to aap ne farmaya : usey khareedo aur aazad kar do kyonke 'walaa' usi ke liye hai jisne aazad kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ( Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se) gosht ka hadiya bheja gaya to unhon ( ghar walon ( ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : ye Barira par sadqa kiya gaya hai, aap ne farmaya : wo uske liye sadqa hai aur hamarey liye hadiya hai. aur usey ikhtiyar diya gaya. Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : uska shauhar aazad tha. Shoba ne kaha : maine phir se uske shauhar ke barey mein unse puchha to unhon-ne kaha : main nahi janta (wo aazad tha ya ghulam . shak ke baghair , yaqin ke sath ki gaee riwayat yahi hai ke wo ghulam tha.)"
3784,"Abu-Dawud ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Shoba ne isi sanad se usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
3785,"Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ka shauhar ghulam tha."
3786,"Rabee-bin-abu-Abdur-Rehman ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke mamley mein teen sunnatein ( mutaiyan ( huin : jab wo aazad hui to uske shauhar ke hawale se usey ikhtiyar diya gaya. usey gosht ka hadiya bheja gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey to handiya choolhey par thi, aap ne khana talab farmaya to aapko roti aur ghar ke saalanon mein se aik saalan pesh kiya gaya, aap ne farmaya : kya maine aag par chadhi handiya nahi dekhi jis mein gosht tha? ghar walon ne jawab diya : kyon nahi, Allah ke rasool ! wo gosht Barira (Raziallahu anhu) par sadqa kiya gaya tha to hamein achchha na laga ke ham aapko usmein se khilaaein . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faraayaa : wo is par sadqa hai aur uski taraf se hamarey liye hadiya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi ( Barira (Raziallahu anhu)) ke barey mein farmaya tha : haq 'walaa' usi ke liye hai jisne aazad kiya."
3787,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne chaha ke aik londi khareed kar aazad karein to uske maalikon ne ( usey bechney se) inkar kiya, siwaey-iske ke haq 'walaa' unka ho. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kahi to aap ne farmaya : ye shart tumhen ( neki se) na rokey , kyonke haq 'walaa' usi ka hai jisne aazad kiya."
3788,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne hamein Abdullah-bin-Dinar se khabar di, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 'walaa' (sarparasti) ko bechney aur hiba (deney,hadiya) karne se mana farmaya, Ibrahim ne kaha : maine Muslim-bin Hajjaj ko ye kehtey huey suna : is hadis mein tamam log Abdullah-bin-Dinar hi par inhisaar (nirbhar) karne waley hain. (sab sanadein unhein par aa kar mil jati hain.)"
3789,"ibne-Uena , Ismail-bin-Jafar , Sufiyan Sory , Shoba , Ubaidullah aur Suhak-bin-Usman sab ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, siwaey-iske ke Ubaidullah se ( abdul-wahaab ( Saqfi ki riwayat ki hui hadis mein sirf khareed aur farokht ka zikr hai, unhon-ne hiba ka zikr nahi kiya."
3790,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (meesaaqe-Madina mein) diiyaton ( uqool ( ki adaaeygi qabeeley ki har shaakh par lazim thehraai, phir aap ne likha : kisi musalman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke kisi (aur ( musalman ki ijazat ke baghair iske ( Maula ( ghulam ko apna Maula ( haqe-'walaa' rakhney wala ( bana ley. phir mujhey khabar di gaee ke aap ne, apne saheefey mein, us shakhs par jo ye kaam karey, laanat bheji."
3791,"Suhel ne apne walid ( Saleh samaan ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne apne aazad karne walon ki ijazat ke baghair kisi (doosri ( qaum ki 'walaa' ikhtiyar ki, is par Allah ki aur farishton ki laanat hai. aur (qiyamat ke roz (us se koi sifarish qabool ki jaeygi na fidya."
3792,"Zayda ne Sulaiman (Aamash) se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne apne aazad karne walon ki ijazat ke baghair kisi (doosri ( qaum ki 'walaa' ikhtiyar ki, is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki laanat hai, aur qiyamat ke din us se koi fidya qabool kya jaeyga na koi sifarish ."
3793,"Sheban ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : jisne apne aazad karne walon ke siwa , unki ijazat ke baghair kisi aur ke sath mawalat ki."
3794,"Ibrahim Taimi ke walid Yazeed bin Sharik se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein khutba diya aur kaha : jiska guman hai ke hamarey paas kitabullah aur us saheefey ke siwa. kaha : wo saheefa unki talwaar ki niyam se latka hua tha. padhi. koi aur cheez hai jisey ham padhtey hain to wo jhoota hai. usmein ( diyat wghaira ke) oonton ki umrein aur zakhmon (ki diyat ( se mutaalliqa kuchh cheezein ( likhi hui ( hain. aur is mein (ye likha hua hai ke) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jabale-eir se lekar Jabale-sor tak Madina haram hai, jisne usmein (gumrahi phailaney ki) koi waardat ki ya waardat karne waley kisi shakhs ko panah di to is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki laanat hai, qiyamat ke din Allah Taala us se koi sifarish qabool karega na badla . tamam musalmanon ki panah aik hai. unka adna aadmi bhi kisi ko panah de sakta hai. jisne apne walid ke siwa kisi ki taraf nisbat ki ya (koi ghulam ( apne aazad karne waley maalikon ke siwa kisi aur ka Maula bana, is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki laanat hai, qiyamat ke din Allah Taala us se koi sifarish qabool karega na fidya."
3795,"Ismail bin abi hakeem ne mujhey Saeed bin Marjana se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne kisi momin gardan ( momin ghulam jiski gardan mein ghulaami ka tauq tha) ko aazad kya, Allah Taala us ( aazad kiye janey waale) ke har uzu (khaas ang) ke badley us ( aazad karne waale) ka wahi uzu (khaas ang) aag se aazad farmaeyga ."
3796,"Ali-bin Husain ne Saeed bin Marjana se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne kisi momin gardan ko aazad kya to Allah Taala uske har uzu (khaas ang) ke badley us ( aazad karne waale) ke aaza mein se wahi uzu (khaas ang) aag se aazad farmaeyga yahan tak ke uski sharmgah ke badley uski sharmgah ko bhi."
3797,"Umar-bin ( Zainul-Aabedeen ( Ali-bin-Husain (bin-Ali-bin-abi-Talib ( ne Saeed-bin-Marjana se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jisne kisi momin ko aazad kiya, Allah Taala uske har uzu  (ang) ke badley (is aazad karne waley ka wahi ( uzu (ang) aag se aazad karega, yahan tak ke uski sharmgah ke badley uski sharmgah ko bhi aazad kar dega."
3798,"Waqid bin-Muhammad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Ali-bin-Husain (bin-Ali-bin-abi-Talib (ke sathi (shagird) Saeed-bin-Marjana ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis musalman ne kisi musalman ko aazad kiya, to Allah Taala uske (aazad kiye janey waale) har uzu (ang) ke badley iske wahi uzu (ang) aag se bacha lega. (Saeed-bin-Marjanane) kaha : jab maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis suni to main nikla aur Ali-bin-Husain ke samney iska tazkira kiya to unhon-ne apna wo ghulam aazad kar diya jis (ko kharidney (ke liye ( Abdullah ( ibne-Jafar ne unhein das hazaar dirham ya aik hazaar Dinar dene ki pesh-kash ! ki thi."
3799,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein jareed ne Suhel se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh samaan ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi betaa walid ka haq ada nahi kar sakta , siwaey-iske ke usey ghulam paaey , usey khareedey aur aazad kar de. ibne-Abi-Sheba ki riwayat mein : koi betaa apne walid ka ke alfaz hain."
3800,"Wakee , Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu Ahmed zubairi sab ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur un sab ne bhi ''koi betaa apne walid ka'' ke alfaz kahey."
